OL,3,CCouncil tax shake-up in Wales put off
OL,4,Cfor another three years
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government has put off plans
OL,7,Fto shake up council tax for another
OL,8,Fthree years.
OL,10,FFinance secretary Rebecca Evans says
OL,11,Fshe has chosen to adopt a slower
OL,12,Ftimetable after carrying out a
OL,13,Fconsultation but that the Welsh
OL,14,FGovernment remains committed to making
OL,15,Fcouncil tax fairer.
OL,17,FReforming council tax was one of the
OL,18,Fmain pledges in Labour's Co-Operation
OL,19,FAgreement with Plaid Cymru, which said
OL,20,Fit was "disappointed" by the
OL,21,Fannouncement.
