OL,3,CCouncil tax shake-up in Wales put off
OL,4,Cfor another three years
OL,6,FMs Evans said 1,676 responses were
OL,7,Freceived from members of the public
OL,8,Fand a range of expert organisations
OL,9,Fduring a phase-two consultation, with
OL,10,F67% of respondents wanting some
OL,11,Fchanges to council tax. 35% opted for
OL,12,Fthe slowest timeframe option, starting
OL,13,Fin 2028, with 24% opting for the
OL,14,Ffastest timetable, from 2025, and 17%
OL,15,Fchoosing staged implementation.
