OL,3,CCouncil tax shake-up in Wales put off
OL,4,Cfor another three years
OL,6,FIn an update to MSs, she said: "Having
OL,7,Flistened carefully to the consultation
OL,8,Fresponses and the broader public
OL,9,Fconversation, I intend to deliver
OL,10,Fcouncil tax reform over a slower
OL,11,Ftimeline in line with the majority
OL,12,Fview of those who responded to our
OL,13,Fconsultation.
OL,15,F"We now plan to introduce the
OL,16,Fstructural reforms to the council tax
OL,17,Fsystem from 2028, although I will
OL,18,Fdeliver other improvements by the end
OL,19,Fof the Senedd term.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
