OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F465A1715797962
OL,3,CCouncil tax shake-up in Wales put off
OL,4,Cfor another three years
OL,6,F"While looking at options for reform,
OL,7,Fwe have also considered the necessity
OL,8,Fof an appropriate transition fund and
OL,9,Fthe immediate implications such a fund
OL,10,Fwould have on the broader financial
OL,11,Fpressures we currently face.
OL,13,F"I believe this approach demonstrates
OL,14,Fa continuing commitment to fair and
OL,15,Fprogressive taxation, as well as this
OL,16,FWelsh Government's commitment to
OL,17,Flistening to the people of Wales.
OL,19,F"The Welsh Government remains
OL,20,Fcommitted to our aim of making council
OL,21,Ftax fairer and more up-to-date."
