OL,3,CCouncil tax shake-up in Wales put off
OL,4,Cfor another three years
OL,6,FWhile council tax in England and
OL,7,FScotland is still charged according to
OL,8,F1991 property values, Wales is the
OL,9,Fonly nation of the UK to have revalued
OL,10,Fcouncil tax but the tax bands are now
OL,11,Fbased on information more than 20
OL,12,Fyears old.
OL,14,FThe Welsh Government is in the process
OL,15,Fof establishing regular revaluation
OL,16,Fcycles in the Local Government Finance
OL,17,F(Wales) Bill which is currently being
OL,18,Fscrutinised by the Senedd.
