OL,6,FMs Evans plans to bring forward an
OL,7,Famendment to the Bill to begin five-
OL,8,Fyearly revaluations from 2028 to keep
OL,9,Fcouncil tax "fair and responsive to
OL,10,Feconomic circumstances, and it
OL,11,Fprovides a regular opportunity for
OL,12,Ftaxpayers to engage with the
OL,13,Frevaluation process, improving the
OL,14,Ftransparency of how things work".
