OL,6,FOn revaluation, her statement added:
OL,7,F"The Valuation Office Agency (VOA) has
OL,8,Fdeveloped new technology in discussion
OL,9,Fwith international experts on
OL,10,Fvaluation methods. We now have systems
OL,11,Fin place which provide comprehensive
OL,12,Fand robust information about up-to-
OL,13,Fdate property values to advance our
OL,14,Fpath to delivery in 2028."
OL,16,FThere are also plans to streamline the
OL,17,Fappeals process, and raise awareness
OL,18,Fof how council tax works and what it
OL,19,Fpays for.
