OL,6,FMs Evans added: Council tax remains a
OL,7,Fcentral part of how we fund local
OL,8,Fgovernment in Wales. Almost everyone
OL,9,Fbenefits in some way from the
OL,10,Fcontribution it makes to the work of
OL,11,Four local authorities.
OL,13,F"However, we have to make sure the way
OL,14,Fwe collect council tax is fair and
OL,15,Fbased on the most consistent and best
OL,16,Finformation that we have available. We
OL,17,Falso need to recognise the financial
OL,18,Fpressures that households are living
OL,19,Fthrough at the moment.
