OL,6,F"I will continue working through these
OL,7,Fchallenges in the years ahead, and I
OL,8,Fam protecting local services as much
OL,9,Fas possible at a time of enormous
OL,10,Fpressure on the Welsh Government's and
OL,11,Flocal government budgets.
OL,13,F"The work I describe above addresses
OL,14,Four commitment to creating a fairer
OL,15,Fcouncil tax system while ensuring that
OL,16,Four arrangements are fair in both
OL,17,Foperation and implementation."
OL,19,FPeredur Owen Griffith, MS the Plaid
OL,20,FCymru spokesperson for local
OL,21,Fgovernment and finance, said:
