OL,6,F"Reforming Council Tax and creating a
OL,7,Ffairer system is a key part of o Plaid
OL,8,FCymru's vision for a fairer and more
OL,9,Fprogressive Wales.
OL,11,FWhilst we've succeeded in ensuring
OL,12,Fthat Welsh Government commits to
OL,13,Freform, we are disappointed that it
OL,14,Fhasn't adopted a more ambitious
OL,15,Ftimetable.
