OL,6,FWe had hoped that Welsh Government
OL,7,Fwould seize the opportunity to move
OL,8,Fquickly help some of the poorest
OL,9,Fhouseholders, currently suffering the
OL,10,Fworst effects of the cost-of-living
OL,11,Fcrisis, and who would have benefited
OL,12,Ffrom lower bills in 2025."
OL,14,FCitizens Advice Cymru said Council Tax
OL,15,Fwas in "desperate" need of reform.
